            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "證監下午公布虛擬資產平台交易代化幣化基金",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">證監會下午將公布允許虛擬資產交易平台交易代幣化基金。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中介機構部的執行董事葉志衡在Web3 Festival中表示，今日下午將公布一項新措施，允許持牌虛擬資產交易平台不僅提供代幣化的證監會認可基金，更可進行交易。他表示， 這是全球首個為代幣化基金在受監管平台交易，提供清晰監管框架的機制。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">葉志衡表示，將首先從貨幣市場基金開始。若經驗良好，將逐步擴展至所有證監會認可授權基金。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15894412-%e8%ad%89%e7%9b%a3%e4%b8%8b%e5%8d%88%e5%85%ac%e5%b8%83%e8%99%9b%e6%93%ac%e8%b3%87%e7%94%a2%e5%b9%b3%e5%8f%b0%e4%ba%a4%e6%98%93%e4%bb%a3%e5%8c%96%e5%b9%a3%e5%8c%96%e5%9f%ba%e9%87%91",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250625_FI_source-web_SFC-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-20 11:54:50",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "工信部提光伏業「兼併重組」反內卷 五大電力集團首度現身座談會",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">工信部、發改委等部門日前聯合召開光伏行業座談會，會上提出將「兼併重組」作為應對行業過度競爭（內卷）的綜合治理手段之一。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">工信部在新聞稿中列明，將全力推進產能調控、標準引領、創新驅動、價格執法、質量監管、兼併重組及知識產權保護等反內卷工作。值得注意的是，此次座談會首次有華能集團、大唐集團、華電集團、國家電力投資集團及國家能源投資集團等五大電力央企參與，工信部自去年以來已合計召開四次光伏行業座談會。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15894416-%e5%b7%a5%e4%bf%a1%e9%83%a8%e6%8f%90%e5%85%89%e4%bc%8f%e6%a5%ad%e3%80%8c%e5%85%bc%e4%bd%b5%e9%87%8d%e7%b5%84%e3%80%8d%e5%8f%8d%e5%85%a7%e5%8d%b7-%e4%ba%94%e5%a4%a7%e9%9b%bb%e5%8a%9b%e9%9b%86%e5%9c%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20240305_FI_source-ap_china-economy_fb.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-20 11:54:50",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滬深兩市半日反彈逾0.5% 寧德時代逆市受壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市今早跟隨外圍反彈，滬深兩市股指半日升逾0.5%，寧德時代(03750)A股(300750.SZ)有股東擬減持，股份應聲受壓。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指今早輕微高開1點即展開一浪高於一浪的走勢，半日低位4051點時仍升不足1點，早市後段最高曾衝上4082點，升31點，至中午收市前升幅仍大致維持在20點以上；滬指中午收報4078點，升26點或0.67%，半日成交7147.23億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指相對跑輸，初段最多曾跌39點，低見14845點，約10分鐘後開始轉升，一度重越萬五關，高見15006點，升121點，中午收市前半小時升幅重新收窄；深指中午收報14974點，升89點或0.6%，成交9911.64億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數也升25點或0.54%，收報4754點；創業板指數微升1點或0.04%，報3679點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250409_FI_source-ap_China-2-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250409_FI_source-ap_China-2-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深市重磅股寧德時代逆市報跌，是拖低深指的主力。寧德時代日前發公告，指出持該公司逾2.84億股A股、持股6.23%的寧波聯合創新能源，擬減持5800萬股A股並就此詢價；寧德時代A股今早裂口低開，中午收報427.3元，跌3.8%，半日成交已達141.34億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15894363-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1%e5%85%a9%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88%e9%80%be0-5-%e5%af%a7%e5%be%b7%e6%99%82%e4%bb%a3%e9%80%86%e5%b8%82%e5%8f%97%e5%a3%93",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-10.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-20 11:39:39",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股向上  最多升232點  AI相關股揚升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股恒指生指數高開後向上，暫時最低報26094，跌66點或0.25%，即反彈向上，最高報26392，升232點或0.88%，現報26373，升213點或0.82%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數升46點或0.92%，報5089點 ; 恒生國企指數報8908，升63點或0.72%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：智譜官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251211_FI_source-web_Zhipu-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：智譜官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251211_FI_source-web_Zhipu-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：智譜官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市現成交1153.87億元。  </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">智譜(02513)現價升14.48%，報1020元，最高見1030元，最低見895元；MINIMAX稀宇(00100)升5.59%，報907元。據The Information指出，中國AI初創公司DeepSeek正與投資者洽談，計劃以100億美元的估值籌集至少3億美元資金。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manycore(00068)升54.09%，報28.66元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">長飛光纖光纜(06869)H股現價升4.27%，報214.8元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">光通信概念齊漲，京信通信(02342)升2.63%，報1.56元；匯聚科技(01729)升3.99%，報21.88元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)升2.64%，報524元; 阿里巴巴(09988)升0.88%，報137.6元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">華虹半導體(01347)升5.14%，報95.15元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">信義光能(00968)升6.55%，報3.09元，為表現最佳藍籌股 ; 中石油(00857)跌2.81%，報10.39元，為表現最差藍籌股。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15894297-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%90%91%e4%b8%8a-%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%9a%e5%8d%87232%e9%bb%9e-ai%e7%9b%b8%e9%97%9c%e8%82%a1%e6%8f%9a%e5%8d%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-6.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-20 11:16:30",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
