            "title": "日股重越59000點 半日升0.97%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日股早市持續向好，日經平均指數重越59000點水平，中午收報59045點，升569點或0.97%。</p>\n</div>",
